WITH latest_day AS (
 SELECT AddressTextHash
 FROM [realtor_lake].[dbo].[listings_silver]
 WHERE source_file = (SELECT MAX(source_file) FROM [realtor_lake].[dbo].[listings_silver])
 AND BuildingType = 'House'
),
d_rank AS (
    SELECT ListingId, MlsNumber, AddressTextHash, AddressText, ListingInsertedDateMT, PriceUnformattedValue, PriceChangeDateUTC, PriceChangeDateTimeStampUTC, PriceChangeDateMT, DENSE_RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY AddressText ORDER BY ListingId) drank
    FROM [realtor_lake].[dbo].[listings_silver]
    WHERE BuildingType = 'House'
)
SELECT d.*
FROM d_rank D
JOIN latest_day l ON l.AddressTextHash = d.AddressTextHash 
--WHERE AddressText = '334 Bridleridge Way SW|Calgary, Alberta T2Y4M6'
WHERE d.AddressTextHash IN (SELECT DISTINCT AddressTextHash FROM d_rank WHERE drank = 2) 
;
-- select top 10 AddressTextHash from [realtor_lake].[dbo].[listings_silver]

SELECT 
 source_file, BuildingType, COUNT(1) cnt, CEILING(AVG(PriceUnformattedValue)) AS avg_price
FROM [realtor_lake].[dbo].[listings_bronze]
--WHERE [source_file] = '2023-08-26'
--   and buildingtype = 'House'
GROUP BY source_file, BuildingType
ORDER BY source_file DESC, BuildingType ASC
 ;
